            <title>[MJAVADOC-129] javadocDirectory config parameter is ignored and default doesn&apos;t work either. </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MJAVADOC-129</link>
                <project id="12317529" key="MJAVADOC">Maven Javadoc Plugin (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;javadoc should pick up the javadoc package.html and overview.html and image files from src/main/javadoc by default. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It will only pick up the src/main/javadoc directory if it is entered in the sourcepath config param. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>linux 2.6, mvn 2.0.6</environment>
